---
// Test page to verify deployment pipeline is working
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Deploy Test</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        background: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem 3rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 { color: #2e2e2e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      p { color: #666; }
      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #22c55e;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <h1>Deploy Test Page</h1>
      <p>If you can see this page, the deployment pipeline is working.</p>
      <p>Built at: <strong>{new Date().toISOString()}</strong></p>
      <span class="badge">Online</span>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
